WEBVTT

00:45.254 --> 00:48.966
PERFECT CROWN

00:59.851 --> 01:01.060
THIS IS A WORK OF FICTION

01:01.061 --> 01:02.980
CHILD ACTORS AND ANIMALS
WERE FILMED SAFELY

01:11.738 --> 01:14.657
Your Royal Highness, is your
scandal with CEO Seong Huiju true?

01:14.658 --> 01:16.659
Why was a doctor called to the hotel?

01:16.660 --> 01:17.994
Would you care to respond?

01:17.995 --> 01:19.620
Are you officially confirming it?

01:19.621 --> 01:21.163
Are the rumors true?

01:21.164 --> 01:22.833
- Is it true?
- Do you acknowledge it?

01:24.251 --> 01:26.210
Oh. It's Seong Huiju!

01:51.194 --> 01:54.072
Prepare yourself to become
the Grand Prince's wife.

01:57.075 --> 01:58.076
You will be up against…

02:01.747 --> 02:03.540
…the whole nation.

02:17.471 --> 02:18.513
Before all that,

02:20.223 --> 02:21.558
shall we see what you can do?

02:28.523 --> 02:29.524
Well then,

02:30.484 --> 02:32.652
how about a generous donation
to the Crown?

02:32.653 --> 02:33.945
Sway public opinion first.

02:35.155 --> 02:37.282
The palace will remain silent.

02:41.995 --> 02:42.996
Hmm.

02:46.166 --> 02:47.626
You had me worried for a second.

02:56.051 --> 02:57.468
Move faster already.

02:57.469 --> 03:00.096
GRAND PRINCE I-AN ENTERS PALACE
WITH CEO SEONG HUIJU

03:00.097 --> 03:04.100
Today, I'm going to show you the trending
"Seong Huiju makeup" tutorial,

03:04.101 --> 03:05.976
the look that stole Prince I-AN's heart.

03:09.147 --> 03:11.607
"COMMONER" SEONG HUIJU ENTERS PALACE
WHAT'S NEXT?

03:32.045 --> 03:35.756
PERFECT CROWN

03:37.467 --> 03:39.511
EPISODE 3
:cue

03:46.726 --> 03:48.061
Welcome, Your Royal Highness.

03:49.271 --> 03:51.064
Her Majesty is looking for you.

03:51.982 --> 03:54.483
- I will pay her a visit tomorrow.
- Your Royal Highness.

03:54.484 --> 03:57.446
Her Majesty has even postponed
her meal and is waiting.

03:58.488 --> 04:00.240
The matter seems rather urgent.

04:01.241 --> 04:02.492
Perhaps you can see her now.

04:06.580 --> 04:08.164
Wait for me. I shall be back.

04:10.208 --> 04:11.543
By myself?

04:26.767 --> 04:27.768
Are you afraid?

04:28.935 --> 04:29.936
No.

04:31.480 --> 04:33.273
Take a nap if you are tired.

04:34.608 --> 04:35.609
Okay.

05:02.093 --> 05:04.095
He's even a good actor.

05:14.523 --> 05:17.983
NOT PRIVY TO CEO'S PRIVATE LIFE,
A CAUSE FOR CELEBRATION IF TRUE

05:17.984 --> 05:19.401
Your Majesty.

05:19.402 --> 05:21.070
Grand Prince I-AN has arrived.

05:32.040 --> 05:33.708
Is such a delay necessary?

05:34.876 --> 05:36.837
- I did not know you were looking for me.
- Not that.

05:37.712 --> 05:40.172
I ask whether such a delay is necessary

05:40.173 --> 05:43.885
before you offer an apology
for causing such a scandal.

05:46.304 --> 05:47.305
I see.

05:48.557 --> 05:51.141
I hear you brought that maiden with you.

05:51.142 --> 05:53.061
I understand the need to align stories,

05:53.562 --> 05:56.106
but did you have to bring her
all the way to the palace?

05:56.606 --> 05:58.191
Have you any intention

05:59.442 --> 06:00.986
of denying it?

06:03.363 --> 06:04.531
It appears I do not.

06:06.116 --> 06:07.367
I plan to confirm

06:08.451 --> 06:11.705
both the tryst at the hotel
and the possibility of marriage.

06:14.708 --> 06:16.459
Are you throwing a tantrum?

06:18.169 --> 06:19.588
Premarital pregnancy…

06:23.884 --> 06:25.176
You can rest assured

06:25.802 --> 06:27.512
that no such tantrum will be thrown.

06:38.899 --> 06:41.401
Your Royal Highness,
Public Affairs has reached out.

06:42.110 --> 06:43.236
What are you doing here?

06:43.820 --> 06:45.864
- Pardon?
- You should be guarding Anhwadang Hall.

06:47.115 --> 06:48.450
To keep an eye on Seong Huiju.

06:49.367 --> 06:50.576
But…

06:50.577 --> 06:51.661
My apologies.

07:02.088 --> 07:03.380
Seong Huiju.

07:03.381 --> 07:04.840
Oh. You're here.

07:04.841 --> 07:06.259
Uncle.

07:08.511 --> 07:10.220
See, I told you it'd be spicy.

07:10.221 --> 07:11.847
Have some water.

07:11.848 --> 07:12.891
I am fine.

07:21.691 --> 07:24.986
Your Majesty,
what are you doing here at this late hour?
:cue

07:25.820 --> 07:27.821
He said he was having trouble sleeping--

07:27.822 --> 07:28.948
I did not ask you.

07:30.325 --> 07:32.452
I was having trouble sleeping.

07:38.958 --> 07:40.418
So I came by.

07:40.919 --> 07:42.420
What does having trouble sleeping

07:44.130 --> 07:45.423
have to do with this?

07:46.424 --> 07:50.095
She said a full belly
would help me fall asleep.

08:01.106 --> 08:02.399
Come in, Court Lady Jung.

08:11.199 --> 08:12.200
Your Majesty.

08:13.910 --> 08:15.912
Shall I escort you
to Queen Mother's quarters?

08:25.839 --> 08:28.007
You couldn't just let him
finish it in peace?

08:32.387 --> 08:34.055
I mean, come on.

08:34.597 --> 08:37.308
A bowl of ramyeon
wouldn't have taken that long to finish.

08:41.187 --> 08:42.689
And if he suffers indigestion?

08:43.523 --> 08:44.858
You would be wholly to blame.

08:45.692 --> 08:47.610
And if Queen Mother is angered?

08:48.194 --> 08:50.320
All that over a measly bowl of ramyeon?

08:50.321 --> 08:51.364
The Queen Mother…

08:53.658 --> 08:54.659
denied the request.

09:02.625 --> 09:03.626
Well…

09:04.127 --> 09:05.628
we expected as much.

09:06.212 --> 09:08.547
But you know, it still doesn't feel great.

09:08.548 --> 09:10.257
Like I'm being bullied by my in-laws.

09:10.258 --> 09:12.093
Wait! Hold on a second.

09:12.927 --> 09:15.013
What will you do
if my in-laws really bully me?

09:16.056 --> 09:18.932
I mean, just look at
how things are unfolding already.

09:18.933 --> 09:22.061
Let's say the Queen Mother
and I got into a fight.

09:22.062 --> 09:24.064
Would you take my side?

09:26.900 --> 09:29.652
Why aren't you answering?

09:30.445 --> 09:32.654
Will you take their side and not mine

09:32.655 --> 09:34.199
because they're your family?

09:39.746 --> 09:40.872
I will take your side.

09:49.380 --> 09:50.381
I must appear

09:51.591 --> 09:52.884
insanely infatuated with you…

10:01.935 --> 10:03.645
…for people to believe

10:05.522 --> 10:07.148
this absurd marriage is genuine.

10:16.741 --> 10:17.908
No, Your Royal Highness.

10:17.909 --> 10:19.993
You cannot let her sleep
in Anhwadang Hall.

10:19.994 --> 10:21.995
We have no choice
with the palace gates shut.

10:21.996 --> 10:24.164
We have the quarters
of the palace attendants.

10:24.165 --> 10:25.667
But she is not a palace attendant.

10:26.709 --> 10:28.544
I shall look for other vacant quarters--

10:28.545 --> 10:29.628
No need.

10:29.629 --> 10:31.881
Get her a change of clothes as well.

10:33.049 --> 10:34.050
Clothes?

10:34.676 --> 10:35.802
Huh?

10:36.469 --> 10:39.472
Can I get something that's 100% cotton?

10:42.016 --> 10:44.144
My skin's a little sensitive.

10:50.984 --> 10:52.610
:cue

10:58.074 --> 10:59.868
Will you not even consider the sofa?

11:00.368 --> 11:03.079
No. This is perfectly fine.

11:08.334 --> 11:10.043
The sofa would be perfectly fine too.

11:10.044 --> 11:13.506
Then you should go. That'd be perfect.

11:53.046 --> 11:54.047
Stop!

11:59.594 --> 12:00.845
My goodness.

12:06.476 --> 12:08.228
- Oh, my.
-  Your Royal Highness.

12:09.479 --> 12:10.771
Your Royal Highness!

12:10.772 --> 12:12.023
Stay still!

12:15.568 --> 12:17.028
Your Royal Highness.

12:19.447 --> 12:21.532
-  Your Royal Highness!
- What? Stay still…

12:23.451 --> 12:24.826
My goodness.

12:24.827 --> 12:26.829
Do you know what time it is right now?

12:27.538 --> 12:29.707
It's unlike you to sleep in like this.

12:35.088 --> 12:37.464
Ms. Seong is already on her way to work.

12:37.465 --> 12:39.092
With a pep in her step, at that.

12:59.237 --> 13:00.822
You didn't change?

13:01.406 --> 13:02.573
No. Something wrong?

13:09.998 --> 13:12.624
Are you trying to show off
that you spent the night out?

13:12.625 --> 13:14.085
Did you not have time to change?

13:14.585 --> 13:17.005
I did have the time, but had no desire to.

13:17.672 --> 13:19.007
I wanted people to know

13:20.258 --> 13:21.509
I didn't go home last night.

13:22.969 --> 13:24.012
Oh.

13:38.568 --> 13:40.320
Are you quite pleased?

13:41.112 --> 13:44.614
Yes, I much prefer this over yakgwa.

13:48.494 --> 13:51.873
Did you sleep well last night?

13:58.212 --> 14:01.799
Did you dream about the late king again?

14:07.513 --> 14:08.514
Hmm.

14:23.738 --> 14:25.114
I am afraid.

14:27.742 --> 14:29.911
Do not worry,
Your Highness the Crown Prince.

14:30.703 --> 14:33.747
- You will have me by your side--
-  You cannot, Your Royal Highness.

14:42.131 --> 14:43.132
Your Royal Highness.

14:44.092 --> 14:46.384
- The wedding rites are about to commence.
- So?

14:46.385 --> 14:49.012
You should take your place out there.

14:52.558 --> 14:54.560
Should His Majesty learn of this…

14:58.314 --> 15:01.525
you will be punished
for dishonoring the Crown Prince.

15:01.526 --> 15:03.236
Are you prepared for that?

15:05.863 --> 15:06.864
Your Royal Highness!

15:11.160 --> 15:12.954
I clearly gave you a chance.

15:14.288 --> 15:15.832
Whatever happens from here on…
:cue

15:18.251 --> 15:19.252
you will have to…

15:21.129 --> 15:22.380
deal with it yourself.

15:27.760 --> 15:29.428
I am scared.

15:32.473 --> 15:35.476
Ah. Do not worry, Your Majesty.

15:35.977 --> 15:40.106
You will always have
your grandfather by your side.

15:43.025 --> 15:44.026
Go on.

15:56.956 --> 15:58.791
FAMILY APPRECIATION
MONTH EVENT REPORT

16:20.521 --> 16:22.564
A ROYAL SCANDAL?
SEONG HUIJU HIT THE JACKPOT…

16:23.733 --> 16:27.445
"A royal child out of wedlock?
That's insane."

16:28.279 --> 16:30.531
That's right. It's totally insane.

16:31.866 --> 16:34.701
"Prince I-AN and Seong Huiju
make a terrible couple."

16:34.702 --> 16:37.205
No, we totally make the hottest couple.

16:38.831 --> 16:40.790
Can you stop reading the comments?

16:40.791 --> 16:42.793
Why? I need to monitor
the situation closely.

16:43.586 --> 16:46.004
"Guys, maybe she has something on him?

16:46.005 --> 16:48.924
Why else would he date a commoner?"

16:48.925 --> 16:50.675
Why do you think, loser?

16:50.676 --> 16:52.845
Because I'm worth dating. That's why.

16:53.512 --> 16:55.264
- You little…
- Here.

16:55.890 --> 16:59.601
The top five trending keywords
are all about you.

16:59.602 --> 17:01.979
Your hotel outfit is already sold out.

17:02.772 --> 17:03.773
Really?

17:05.524 --> 17:06.733
Call the PR team.

17:06.734 --> 17:08.777
The PR team? Why?

17:08.778 --> 17:09.779
Why else?

17:10.446 --> 17:13.449
It's time to take back
the number-one spot in sales.

17:14.575 --> 17:16.535
How can you even
think about that right now?

17:17.828 --> 17:19.287
It's marriage, not retirement.

17:23.668 --> 17:25.753
Oh. Jeongwoo?

17:26.420 --> 17:27.421
Hello, sir.

17:28.172 --> 17:30.465
-  Isn't he so handsome?
- Super handsome!

17:30.466 --> 17:33.176
This is my first time seeing
Prime Minister Min in person.

17:33.177 --> 17:35.387
He looks like a total celebrity.

17:35.388 --> 17:37.180
Right. But what's he doing here?

17:37.181 --> 17:38.390
Maybe because of the scandal?

17:38.391 --> 17:40.851
- Oh! That must be--
- Why is no one working?

17:43.688 --> 17:46.148
You're really going to marry him?

17:46.899 --> 17:48.608
- Yeah.
- His Royal Highness?

17:48.609 --> 17:50.110
Yeah.

17:50.111 --> 17:51.737
I thought you two had just met.

17:52.363 --> 17:53.905
Can't you just stick to dating?

17:53.906 --> 17:56.284
But I want to be with him all the time.

17:57.118 --> 17:59.787
-  Huiju…
- I want to wake up next to him

18:00.413 --> 18:01.455
every day.

18:04.000 --> 18:06.209
I hear the royal family

18:06.210 --> 18:08.629
wants to marry him off to someone else.

18:10.715 --> 18:14.051
That's why I have to marry him right now.

18:14.635 --> 18:16.053
While you're the Prime Minister.

18:21.267 --> 18:22.602
I need you to get

18:24.020 --> 18:25.021
my marriage approved.

18:34.405 --> 18:37.325
We're planning to invite
the top 300 patrons in the country.

18:37.908 --> 18:40.161
-  What are the criteria?
- Your Royal Highness.

18:54.717 --> 18:57.218
The Queen Mother has taken to her sickbed.

18:57.219 --> 18:58.595
All of a sudden?

18:58.596 --> 19:01.139
Perhaps it's a ploy
to prevent an official statement.

19:01.140 --> 19:04.143
The palace cannot speak of celebrations
while a royal elder lies ill.

19:11.317 --> 19:12.818
JUNIOR ALUM

19:14.028 --> 19:15.196
Understood. You may leave.

19:20.910 --> 19:22.328
Your Royal Highness!

19:23.829 --> 19:25.456
I hear you fine. Lower your voice.

19:26.290 --> 19:27.416
Did you read the article?

19:29.293 --> 19:30.670
Right before it was pulled.

19:31.462 --> 19:33.296
It was taken down at lightning speed.

19:33.297 --> 19:35.173
The Queen Mother has been very busy.

19:35.174 --> 19:37.258
I guess even nobles can move quickly

19:37.259 --> 19:38.636
when they want to.

19:39.679 --> 19:40.680
:cue

19:42.973 --> 19:43.974
Seong Huiju?

19:44.517 --> 19:45.518
Oh?

19:46.727 --> 19:48.061
You sly fox!

19:48.062 --> 19:50.022
You dare try to seduce His Royal Highness!

19:51.065 --> 19:52.692
- "Fox"?
- Yeah, you fox!

19:53.442 --> 19:56.361
- Oh, my gosh!
- Stay away from His Royal Highness!

19:56.362 --> 19:58.906
- Get lost!
- Hey, good job.

20:00.825 --> 20:01.991
Seong Huiju?

20:01.992 --> 20:03.661
Should we? Should we not?

20:04.328 --> 20:05.495
Come here, you brats.

20:05.496 --> 20:08.290
- We could throw them all.
- "Come here, you brats!"

20:10.418 --> 20:11.961
Get over here now!

20:27.727 --> 20:28.728
Your Royal Highness.

20:31.355 --> 20:32.647
What is all that?

20:32.648 --> 20:34.607
Is it not obvious? These are your duties.

20:34.608 --> 20:36.152
- All of it?
- All of it.

20:38.195 --> 20:40.780
- That cannot be true.
- It most certainly is.

20:40.781 --> 20:44.368
These are the duties you are
to carry out on His Majesty's behalf.

20:45.035 --> 20:48.413
These are the Queen Mother's… Goodness.
This stack is quite heavy.

20:48.414 --> 20:51.542
These are the Queen Mother's duties
you are to carry out

20:52.251 --> 20:53.626
in her absence.

20:53.627 --> 20:56.338
And these are your duties
that accumulated while you were away.

20:57.006 --> 20:58.798
- You got this.
- Get out.

20:58.799 --> 21:00.092
Yes, sir.

21:00.676 --> 21:02.720
Let's go. Off we go.

21:06.849 --> 21:10.185
You little brats should be in school
with your noses in books.

21:10.186 --> 21:11.687
Eyes down!

21:12.897 --> 21:15.565
Does Prince I-AN put food on your table?

21:15.566 --> 21:17.776
He may not feed us, but he gives us money.

21:17.777 --> 21:20.196
- Right.
- We're royal scholarship students.

21:20.988 --> 21:23.031
That money was for your studies.

21:23.032 --> 21:26.160
Do you think he wanted you to spend
that money buying eggs to throw?

21:26.827 --> 21:27.953
And you, Hyerin.

21:28.496 --> 21:30.789
Why did you assume I seduced him?

21:30.790 --> 21:31.873
Isn't it obvious?

21:31.874 --> 21:33.166
Why, you little…

21:33.167 --> 21:36.002
So young and already full of prejudice.

21:36.003 --> 21:37.880
If I had it my way,

21:38.631 --> 21:42.468
I'd give you hell and take legal action
for pulling something like this…

21:44.011 --> 21:45.179
Come here.

21:46.305 --> 21:47.556
But right now,

21:48.140 --> 21:50.559
your big sis here has
a major undertaking ahead of her.

21:51.227 --> 21:53.354
So I'll let it slide just this once.

21:54.063 --> 21:55.064
Got it?

21:56.565 --> 21:58.400
- Answer me!
- Yes, ma'am!

22:01.987 --> 22:03.446
Off you go.

22:03.447 --> 22:04.824
Almighty God.

22:05.991 --> 22:08.160
Please have mercy on us,

22:09.161 --> 22:10.788
forgive us our sins,

22:11.872 --> 22:15.543
and bring us to everlasting life.

22:17.044 --> 22:18.045
Amen.

22:21.841 --> 22:23.092
Amen.

22:25.302 --> 22:27.388
You said you couldn't come for a while.

22:28.681 --> 22:31.809
I heard my friend is getting married,
so I came to pray.

22:33.143 --> 22:36.438
That friend is very lucky to have you
praying for her happiness.

22:37.022 --> 22:38.023
I'm not so sure.

22:38.983 --> 22:40.317
I prayed for something sinful.

22:41.819 --> 22:42.987
Something sinful?

22:44.905 --> 22:46.115
I do not feel inclined

22:47.032 --> 22:48.367
to congratulate her.

23:01.255 --> 23:03.924
But I don't want to stop her either.

23:10.097 --> 23:11.640
Even if I don't think it's right…

23:12.558 --> 23:14.058
Damn it.

23:14.059 --> 23:16.228
Where did that punk hide it?

23:16.812 --> 23:18.522
If that's what she wants…

23:20.441 --> 23:22.358
- Ma'am.
-  Hey, Jeongwoo.

23:22.359 --> 23:23.818
Are you running an errand?

23:23.819 --> 23:26.404
Yes.

23:26.405 --> 23:28.406
Principal Kim was looking for you earlier.

23:28.407 --> 23:29.658
Did you see him?

23:30.659 --> 23:31.869
…I have to let her.

23:32.578 --> 23:33.787
Found it.

23:36.498 --> 23:37.499
Got it.

23:51.430 --> 23:52.473
:cue

24:04.526 --> 24:07.738
I mean, how did those brats
even get past security?

24:08.656 --> 24:11.450
You have to hand it
to the high schoolers in this country.

24:20.918 --> 24:21.919
Father?

24:34.098 --> 24:37.142
Can I get you anything?

24:40.187 --> 24:41.355
Don't bother. Sit.

24:50.239 --> 24:51.739
About that scandal…

24:51.740 --> 24:53.409
No need to explain.

24:54.868 --> 24:58.788
- You're not curious?
- There's nothing to be curious about.

24:58.789 --> 24:59.790
I'm sure

25:00.290 --> 25:02.584
it's just a cheap stunt
you pulled for attention.

25:05.379 --> 25:06.547
Then why are you here?

25:11.135 --> 25:12.136
It's nearly…

25:13.637 --> 25:15.180
Taeju's mother's death anniversary.

25:17.016 --> 25:18.934
I was wondering if you even remembered.

25:22.646 --> 25:23.647
Ma'am.

25:27.818 --> 25:30.029
She's been standing
outside the house for hours,

25:30.654 --> 25:32.489
but she refuses to talk.

25:33.073 --> 25:36.076
Then you should've reported her
to the police, not brought her inside.

25:36.702 --> 25:37.910
Send her away.

25:37.911 --> 25:40.831
How can we just send away a child
in the middle of the night?

25:43.083 --> 25:45.669
Little one, are you lost?

25:48.213 --> 25:49.381
What's your name?

25:53.594 --> 25:55.012
You don't want to say?

25:58.348 --> 25:59.683
I am

26:00.267 --> 26:01.935
Lee Jooyeon's daughter.

26:07.566 --> 26:08.734
You're my dad…

26:09.651 --> 26:10.652
aren't you?

26:23.916 --> 26:25.792
- Honey! Honey!
- Mom!

26:25.793 --> 26:28.127
- Ma'am! Wake up, ma'am!
- Honey!

26:28.128 --> 26:30.422
- Honey!
- Ma'am!

26:30.964 --> 26:33.216
- Ma'am! Oh, dear goodness!
- Mom, wake up!

26:33.217 --> 26:35.802
Since the day your mother abandoned you…

26:35.803 --> 26:37.178
-  Ma'am.
- Mommy!

26:37.179 --> 26:38.972
…our lives fell into despair.

26:46.980 --> 26:48.523
CERTIFICATE OF AWARD

26:48.524 --> 26:50.900
Buy me a bike too.

26:50.901 --> 26:53.570
The same one as Taeju.

26:56.198 --> 26:58.534
You dared to be greedy…

26:59.118 --> 27:00.327
REPORT CARD

27:01.328 --> 27:03.079
I want a building too.

27:03.080 --> 27:04.997
One that's taller than Taeju's.

27:04.998 --> 27:06.250
So greedy…

27:07.251 --> 27:08.334
STOCK PRICE ANALYSIS

27:08.335 --> 27:10.003
Amend your will, Father.

27:10.671 --> 27:12.004
In my favor.

27:12.005 --> 27:13.632
Your greed was relentless!

27:20.305 --> 27:22.139
Keep your hands off the company.

27:22.140 --> 27:23.266
And if I don't?

27:23.267 --> 27:24.976
I'll have no choice but to act.

27:26.812 --> 27:29.063
- What? Are you going to disown me?
- Why not?

27:29.064 --> 27:30.356
Listen, Mr. Seong Hyeonguk.

27:30.357 --> 27:32.191
You dare call your father by his name?

27:32.192 --> 27:33.694
You just said you'd disown me.

27:34.528 --> 27:36.113
Then you wouldn't be my dad anyway.

27:37.614 --> 27:40.575
So, Mr. Seong Hyeonguk, to summarize,

27:40.576 --> 27:42.159
I shouldn't bother acting out

27:42.160 --> 27:45.163
because it'll all be
Taeju's in the end, right?

27:45.664 --> 27:47.498
Seong Taeju will be the ultimate winner.

27:47.499 --> 27:49.543
Taeju is so awesome!

27:50.043 --> 27:51.253
That's the gist.
:cue

27:51.920 --> 27:52.921
Right?

27:53.881 --> 27:56.883
I should just kill Taeju
and secure my spot in hell.

27:56.884 --> 27:58.050
Seong Huiju!

27:58.051 --> 28:00.929
Anyone who ever tried to pick a fight
with me was exactly like you.

28:01.722 --> 28:04.223
They'd stack the deck
so they couldn't help but win,

28:04.224 --> 28:06.351
and put me in a spot
where I was bound to lose.

28:08.103 --> 28:09.438
I guess they weren't confident

28:10.063 --> 28:11.523
they could win on equal terms.

28:16.153 --> 28:17.154
But you know what?

28:17.654 --> 28:18.989
It's fine.

28:19.615 --> 28:21.366
I'm used to going up against

28:22.451 --> 28:23.576
people like that.

28:23.577 --> 28:25.077
You just won't quit.

28:25.078 --> 28:26.079
I wish you…

28:26.955 --> 28:27.956
all the best.

28:29.374 --> 28:30.918
Though I'm sure you'll lose anyway.

29:07.579 --> 29:09.748
PRINCE

29:21.051 --> 29:22.677
Sorry for hanging up on you earlier--

29:22.678 --> 29:23.929
Are you okay?

29:27.432 --> 29:28.600
Are you all right?

29:32.104 --> 29:33.897
Seong Huiju, can you not hear me?

29:35.941 --> 29:37.776
Can I call you back tomorrow?

29:38.694 --> 29:39.695
What?

29:40.404 --> 29:41.738
I'm a little busy right now.

29:43.073 --> 29:44.157
I'll call you tomorrow.

29:59.881 --> 30:02.134
JUNIOR ALUM

30:43.508 --> 30:46.011
CERTIFICATE OF AWARD

30:59.107 --> 31:00.191
HAPPY BIRTHDAY, TAEJU

31:00.192 --> 31:01.818
HOPE YOU GROW UP
STRONG AND HEALTHY

31:08.575 --> 31:10.577
Buy me a bike too.

31:11.578 --> 31:13.955
The same one as Taeju.

31:29.137 --> 31:30.597
REPORT CARD

31:37.312 --> 31:38.730
I want a building too.

31:39.648 --> 31:41.024
One that's taller than Taeju's.
:cue

31:48.323 --> 31:49.991
Amend your will, Father.

31:50.575 --> 31:51.827
In my favor.

32:08.885 --> 32:09.970
Who is it?

32:13.849 --> 32:15.183
Someone lost their damn mind.

32:15.767 --> 32:17.310
Who the hell is it at this hour…

32:21.106 --> 32:22.274
Damn it.

32:31.074 --> 32:36.788
♪ Teatime for His Royal Highness! ♪

32:37.914 --> 32:38.915
Your Royal Highness?

32:39.624 --> 32:41.710
Wait, are we playing hide and seek?

32:43.712 --> 32:44.879
What are you doing here?

32:44.880 --> 32:46.714
Wait, are you allowed to be here?

32:46.715 --> 32:49.300
Hold on. Did anyone see you?

32:49.301 --> 32:50.427
Where's Aide Choi?

32:51.136 --> 32:52.304
You play baseball at home?

32:56.600 --> 33:00.270
I have one too many enemies, you see.

33:05.650 --> 33:06.734
Oh.

33:06.735 --> 33:07.736
Wait.

33:08.361 --> 33:11.280
How did you even get here?

33:11.281 --> 33:12.990
Wait, did you come here alone?

33:12.991 --> 33:13.992
Yeah.

33:15.118 --> 33:16.494
You can't just…

33:21.875 --> 33:23.084
Let me get this straight.

33:24.211 --> 33:25.962
You picked these up yourself?

33:37.933 --> 33:39.099
THE SEONG HUIJU COMBO

33:39.100 --> 33:40.310
I will have this one.

33:42.270 --> 33:43.897
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

33:45.106 --> 33:47.067
"Seduce the Prince" Seong Huiju Combo.

33:48.026 --> 33:49.027
It seemed popular.

34:11.716 --> 34:12.717
Seriously?

34:13.218 --> 34:16.221
Couldn't you have left
after you finished your work?

34:25.605 --> 34:27.565
- What is it?
- Just a bit amazed.

34:28.358 --> 34:29.484
By what?

34:30.277 --> 34:31.820
I came because you sounded so down.

34:32.612 --> 34:35.365
But seeing you eat,
you seem perfectly fine.

34:41.162 --> 34:42.371
I was a little down.

34:42.372 --> 34:45.417
I was dragged
through the mud all day, you see.

34:46.376 --> 34:49.044
I was barraged
with hate comments on social media.

34:49.045 --> 34:51.630
My father suddenly threatened
to disown me.

34:51.631 --> 34:52.632
Oh, that's right.

34:53.133 --> 34:56.719
I even got egged by your fans today.

34:56.720 --> 34:59.347
I totally forgot to ask
if those eggs were antibiotic-free.

35:00.015 --> 35:01.265
You got "egged"?

35:01.266 --> 35:02.850
Yeah. Two eggs, no less.

35:02.851 --> 35:06.187
Those little pip-squeaks were
so damn strong for no reason.

35:07.272 --> 35:08.772
- It still hurts.
- Here?

35:08.773 --> 35:10.275
Yeah. Just downstairs.

35:12.027 --> 35:13.612
Are you hurt?

35:17.115 --> 35:18.158
Are you hurt anywhere?

35:19.117 --> 35:21.119
:cue

35:53.985 --> 35:55.403
An investigation is required.

36:00.617 --> 36:02.034
They're coming right now?

36:02.035 --> 36:03.620
That's what I said. Now, move it!

36:11.544 --> 36:13.546
She will be staying here
for the time being.

36:20.470 --> 36:22.972
She has been receiving
a troublesome amount of attention.

36:24.057 --> 36:25.350
I was concerned.

36:26.101 --> 36:27.227
So you were…

36:28.353 --> 36:29.938
concerned.

36:30.730 --> 36:31.897
And my instructions?

36:31.898 --> 36:34.150
Everything is ready, Your Royal Highness.

36:41.032 --> 36:42.033
Oh!

36:49.165 --> 36:50.750
Maybe that's a bit too close?

37:05.640 --> 37:07.559
Please make yourself at home.

37:09.018 --> 37:11.479
What should I call you?

37:12.272 --> 37:13.939
- Pardon?
- How should I address you?

37:13.940 --> 37:15.775
Uh…

37:17.736 --> 37:20.946
I am Yeongmun of the Kim Family,
the steward of this residence.

37:20.947 --> 37:23.825
Feel free to call me Steward Kim.

37:25.201 --> 37:27.078
Steward?  Hmm.

37:27.912 --> 37:28.913
Yes, ma'am.

37:29.622 --> 37:30.789
Steward.

37:32.667 --> 37:34.668
It's late, so I will leave you to rest.

37:34.669 --> 37:38.422
I will give you a proper tour
of the property tomorrow.

37:38.423 --> 37:39.674
All right.

37:45.180 --> 37:46.306
Just a second.

37:47.640 --> 37:51.186
How shall I address you?

37:51.811 --> 37:53.188
Ah.

37:57.901 --> 38:01.862
I prefer Ms. Seong or Executive Director,
but you can call me by my name.

38:01.863 --> 38:04.365
You're not my employee, after all.

38:07.160 --> 38:08.161
Then, I shall

38:09.162 --> 38:10.455
address you as Your Ladyship.

38:11.998 --> 38:13.666
"Your Ladyship"?

38:14.876 --> 38:16.044
Well then.

38:27.013 --> 38:28.889
I was at the palace yesterday,

38:28.890 --> 38:31.308
and today, the prince's private residence.

38:40.568 --> 38:41.820
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

38:42.403 --> 38:43.571
Do you like your room?

38:44.906 --> 38:45.907
I mean, it's nice.

38:46.407 --> 38:48.492
It feels like I'm on
a historical drama set.

38:49.619 --> 38:51.287
Why aren't you sleeping?

38:51.830 --> 38:52.956
I have some work to do.

38:55.959 --> 38:57.210
Do you want me to help?

39:52.307 --> 39:54.893
So am I really going to live here now?

39:56.352 --> 39:58.104
Well, it's just that

39:58.646 --> 40:01.065
I'm quite an independent woman.

40:01.566 --> 40:03.401
I find this bustling environment…

40:04.319 --> 40:05.695
a bit bothersome, shall I say?

40:06.195 --> 40:07.739
It's so far from work too.

40:09.532 --> 40:11.117
Shouldn't you be more "bothered"

40:11.868 --> 40:15.370
if I were to leave you in harm's way
when I'm supposedly infatuated with you?

40:15.371 --> 40:16.663
Commute aside.

40:16.664 --> 40:18.291
Okay.

40:21.878 --> 40:23.171
:cue

40:24.422 --> 40:25.465
By the way…

40:27.216 --> 40:28.592
You wanted to help.

40:28.593 --> 40:29.594
Is this you helping?

40:30.511 --> 40:32.889
I don't know anything
about the royal ancestral rites.

40:33.389 --> 40:35.350
I've never even attended
any of my family's.

40:43.942 --> 40:45.234
What do you want to know?

40:47.987 --> 40:49.237
Why are you marrying me?

40:50.698 --> 40:52.991
Isn't it a bit late to be asking that?

40:52.992 --> 40:55.577
We only made the decision yesterday.

40:55.578 --> 40:57.789
Why can't I be a little curious today?

40:59.707 --> 41:00.792
You have a lot of money.

41:01.459 --> 41:03.211
The richest in the country, no less.

41:05.546 --> 41:07.089
Is that your reason?

41:07.090 --> 41:08.507
The most important reason.

41:08.508 --> 41:11.176
It would help the royal family,
always under fire

41:11.177 --> 41:13.178
for squandering taxpayers' money.

41:15.098 --> 41:16.891
And what a noble reason it is.

41:17.392 --> 41:18.893
Second.

41:21.896 --> 41:22.939
Beauty.

41:23.940 --> 41:24.983
"Beauty"?

41:25.566 --> 41:28.361
Oh, I guess that finally broke through.

41:30.405 --> 41:32.072
- Third.
- What? What now?

41:32.073 --> 41:33.740
Because my family doesn't overstep?

41:33.741 --> 41:35.785
If I say I wish to ascend the throne,

41:37.996 --> 41:40.123
all would condemn me and hurl insults.

41:44.460 --> 41:45.461
But I believe

41:46.713 --> 41:47.922
you would understand me.

42:11.988 --> 42:14.406
The Inner Court Banquet
is still some time away.

42:14.407 --> 42:17.242
Yet I am already being pressed
to make a decision.

42:17.243 --> 42:19.286
It appears they are quite anxious,

42:19.287 --> 42:21.496
as they need to finalize
the guest list soon.

42:21.497 --> 42:25.084
Does Your Majesty have any criteria
in mind for the guest list?

42:25.668 --> 42:26.794
I'm not sure.

42:30.214 --> 42:33.426
Those with exemplary character,
admirable talents,

42:34.969 --> 42:36.387
and innate nobility?

42:39.390 --> 42:41.183
Would that suffice?

42:51.402 --> 42:53.321
I must cancel today's itinerary.

42:54.155 --> 42:55.447
Pardon?

42:55.448 --> 42:56.656
But they already--

42:56.657 --> 42:58.076
Surely there should be no issue.

43:01.287 --> 43:02.997
I am indisposed, after all.

43:18.387 --> 43:20.264
Your Ladyship, please wake up.

43:25.311 --> 43:26.604
Your Ladyship, wake up.

43:28.272 --> 43:29.273
Wait, hold on.

43:31.025 --> 43:33.401
How dare you storm in here! Hey, you!

43:33.402 --> 43:34.569
Youngseon!

43:34.570 --> 43:36.948
Why that little prick…

43:39.117 --> 43:40.284
What in the world?

43:52.672 --> 43:53.755
What's this about?

43:53.756 --> 43:57.551
Cooperate with the Junghwajeon Hall
fire investigation, please.

43:57.552 --> 43:58.970
"Cooperate"?

44:02.640 --> 44:04.016
At the Royal Birthday Banquet,

44:04.892 --> 44:07.645
you entered a restricted area
of the palace, didn't you?

44:08.771 --> 44:10.731
I did get lost at one point.

44:11.649 --> 44:12.650
But what about it?

44:13.401 --> 44:15.778
Are you suggesting
I started the fire or something?

44:16.362 --> 44:17.904
Nothing has been ruled out yet.

44:18.990 --> 44:22.618
You'll need to give a detailed account
of what you did and who you met there.

44:23.369 --> 44:25.204
What exactly am I supposed to explain?

44:29.125 --> 44:30.750
What was that?

44:30.751 --> 44:31.752
You stay here.

44:32.503 --> 44:34.964
You've publicly stated,
"The royal family is a money pit.

44:35.464 --> 44:38.593
Someone should abolish the Crown.
Let's bring out the guillotine."

44:39.135 --> 44:40.136
Is that correct?

44:43.890 --> 44:44.973
Do you have a warrant?

44:47.185 --> 44:50.228
Under the Royalty
and Specialist Protection Law,

44:50.229 --> 44:53.649
suspects of royal threats
may be investigated prior to a warrant.

44:54.817 --> 44:55.860
Get started.

44:56.819 --> 44:58.613
Hold on. Take your shoes off.

44:59.780 --> 45:01.324
No, you can't take that!

45:07.496 --> 45:09.623
What do you think you're doing?

45:09.624 --> 45:11.666
- Hold on a second.
- You can't take this!

45:11.667 --> 45:13.460
-  What are you doing?
- Move!

45:13.461 --> 45:16.130
-  Is this really necessary?
-  Please step aside.

45:17.590 --> 45:18.882
What are you doing?

45:18.883 --> 45:20.843
- This is insane.
-  Why are you doing this?
:cue

45:27.892 --> 45:29.142
Damn it. What now?

45:29.143 --> 45:30.936
Gosh, you're working so hard.

45:30.937 --> 45:32.103
Have you eaten yet?

45:32.104 --> 45:33.813
- You need to eat something.
- I'm fine.

45:33.814 --> 45:35.565
Let's fill that belly first.

45:35.566 --> 45:39.194
This is His Royal Highness's favorite,
so let's have a taste.

45:39.195 --> 45:40.654
Come on. Take a seat.

45:40.655 --> 45:43.699
Sit down. Let's have a bite while we chat.

45:44.200 --> 45:45.951
Go on. Just try one.

45:48.913 --> 45:52.123
Your Ladyship,
you need to eat something too.

45:52.124 --> 45:54.000
Can't be questioned on an empty stomach.

45:54.001 --> 45:55.877
- Go on. It's still warm.
- No thanks.

45:55.878 --> 45:57.088
- Come on!
- Stop it.

45:57.672 --> 45:59.215
I'm calling His Royal Highness.

46:01.175 --> 46:02.677
Why isn't he picking up?

46:03.886 --> 46:05.137
He probably won't answer.

46:05.805 --> 46:06.888
What?

46:06.889 --> 46:09.308
Cell phones are not allowed
during the ritual.

46:10.351 --> 46:11.352
Ritual?

46:11.978 --> 46:13.062
As in ancestral rites?

46:34.583 --> 46:36.668
Ms. Do. You're running, right?

46:36.669 --> 46:38.586
Yes, I'm running.

46:38.587 --> 46:40.505
What a hell of a way to spend the weekend.

46:40.506 --> 46:42.966
What choice do I have?
You're the only one I can trust.

46:42.967 --> 46:44.384
Forget all that.

46:44.385 --> 46:46.095
Prepare to give me a hefty bonus.

46:46.679 --> 46:47.722
Hang up now.

46:50.182 --> 46:51.183
I got this.

46:53.060 --> 46:54.394
She won't get in.

46:54.395 --> 46:55.854
Why not?

46:55.855 --> 46:57.106
She's a civilian.

46:57.982 --> 47:00.901
Civilians may enter Jongmyo Shrine
only on special days.

47:02.862 --> 47:03.863
Come on.

47:05.823 --> 47:08.033
Oh. Oh!

47:08.034 --> 47:09.576
Huh?

47:09.577 --> 47:11.746
ROYAL PROTECTION BRANCH

47:29.430 --> 47:30.431
Shall we?

47:42.151 --> 47:43.444
-  Hurry up, ma'am.
- Hold on…

47:44.278 --> 47:46.197
My goodness.

47:47.156 --> 47:49.324
Wait. I can't believe this.

47:49.325 --> 47:51.368
- Please let me in this once.
- No, you can't.

47:51.369 --> 47:53.203
I'm from Castle Beauty.

47:53.204 --> 47:54.913
I need to see His Royal Highness.

47:54.914 --> 47:55.998
We already told you no.

47:56.499 --> 47:57.874
Just leave already!

47:57.875 --> 47:59.585
How can I when I know he's in there?

48:04.131 --> 48:05.674
Ms. Do!

48:06.175 --> 48:08.803
Ms. Do!

48:09.387 --> 48:11.846
Ms. Do! Oh, Ms. Do!

48:11.847 --> 48:13.265
Ms. Do…

48:17.144 --> 48:18.895
We come by order of the Grand Prince.

48:18.896 --> 48:21.649
GRAND PRINCE I-AN

48:41.252 --> 48:42.253
Good heavens!

48:44.755 --> 48:45.922
That…

48:45.923 --> 48:47.882
Isn't that the Grand Prince's hopae?

48:47.883 --> 48:49.885
Why was that precious thing in the toilet?

48:51.512 --> 48:53.097
- Steward Kim.
- Yes?

48:55.891 --> 48:57.268
Please take it to Jongmyo.

48:58.227 --> 49:00.479
- Pardon?
- Just in case.

49:01.856 --> 49:02.898
I'm counting on you.

49:03.607 --> 49:04.608
You got this!

49:07.862 --> 49:08.863
Good luck!

49:10.239 --> 49:11.406
Good? Step aside.

49:11.407 --> 49:13.951
I knew it!
You could've just let me pass earlier!
:cue

49:20.666 --> 49:22.418
Where are you going? It's this way.

49:24.044 --> 49:25.921
That bonus better be a generous one.

49:26.672 --> 49:27.715
I'm so exhausted.

50:19.683 --> 50:22.227
Oh, dear. He can't step out
while the ritual is underway.

50:22.228 --> 50:24.647
It's already started.

50:33.113 --> 50:34.156
Oh.

50:35.491 --> 50:37.618
- If he can't leave…
- Yes?

50:38.118 --> 50:39.495
…we can go in instead.

50:40.788 --> 50:41.997
What?

50:54.218 --> 50:55.301
Huh?

50:55.302 --> 50:57.136
-  We need to go.
- What?

50:57.137 --> 50:59.222
- We need to go.
- Pardon?

50:59.223 --> 51:00.224
We need to go.

51:01.058 --> 51:02.977
- How did you even get in here?
- Quiet…

51:04.979 --> 51:06.230
We need to go.

51:07.648 --> 51:09.191
We need to go right now.

51:13.988 --> 51:15.197
So…

51:16.448 --> 51:18.325
You're going to question me at the palace?

51:26.166 --> 51:27.375
Seong Huiju!

51:35.759 --> 51:37.136
Mr. Jung.

51:38.178 --> 51:39.430
Your Royal Highness.

51:40.806 --> 51:43.934
I heard the Royal Ancestral Rite
was being held at Jongmyo Shrine today.

51:44.518 --> 51:46.937
- What brings you by?
- His Majesty is presiding over it.

51:48.772 --> 51:50.524
But what business have you here?

51:51.900 --> 51:54.445
Without authorization
from either His Majesty or me.

51:57.239 --> 51:58.782
I gave the authorization.

52:08.000 --> 52:11.128
As I heard the prime suspect
in the arson case had been identified.

52:11.754 --> 52:12.755
And since she is…

52:15.007 --> 52:17.593
considered a flight risk
and may destroy evidence.

52:19.595 --> 52:21.847
But I did not know that you would be here.

52:23.307 --> 52:24.683
Is there actually any evidence?

52:25.934 --> 52:28.395
As if insulting the Crown
with such insolent attire

52:29.021 --> 52:31.732
and threatening others
within the palace were not enough,

52:32.483 --> 52:33.525
I hear she was absent

52:34.818 --> 52:36.487
at the time of the incident.

52:37.154 --> 52:38.863
Does that constitute evidence?

52:38.864 --> 52:40.156
Perhaps not.

52:40.157 --> 52:42.743
But it should be enough to tarnish…

52:44.453 --> 52:45.871
her reputation

52:46.455 --> 52:48.290
or her company's reputation.

52:48.999 --> 52:50.167
Wait, my company?

52:53.754 --> 52:55.089
Then have me questioned too.

52:58.634 --> 53:01.136
Every circumstance
that casts suspicion on her

53:02.304 --> 53:04.139
applies to me as well.

53:13.691 --> 53:15.359
Will your confidence hold?

53:17.444 --> 53:18.570
I wonder
:cue

53:20.614 --> 53:21.865
if yours will hold.

53:36.338 --> 53:38.048
Ms. Seong!

53:41.885 --> 53:43.262
Oh, Your Royal Highness!

53:43.887 --> 53:45.139
- Summon a physician.
- I-AN.

53:47.015 --> 53:49.518
Feel free to come to Anhwadang Hall
for the questioning.

53:52.271 --> 53:54.272
Summon a physician!

53:54.273 --> 53:55.524
Hurry.

53:57.151 --> 53:58.527
Are you all right, Ms. Seong?

54:23.844 --> 54:24.845
Open your eyes.

54:28.015 --> 54:29.808
Wow.

54:30.768 --> 54:32.018
Wow, we totally slayed!

54:32.019 --> 54:33.102
Slayed, my foot.

54:34.438 --> 54:35.898
How could you agree to come here?

54:37.107 --> 54:39.984
That Mr. Jung or whatever
practically dragged me out.

54:39.985 --> 54:40.986
How could I resist?

54:45.574 --> 54:46.575
So…

54:47.618 --> 54:49.244
will I be going to prison?

54:51.413 --> 54:52.497
Does that scare you?

54:53.916 --> 54:55.291
Me?

54:55.292 --> 54:57.418
I'm Seong Huiju of Castle Group.

54:57.419 --> 55:00.005
Prosecutor investigations
and search-and-seizure raids…

55:00.506 --> 55:01.507
Stuff like that

55:02.090 --> 55:04.718
is practically an annual event.

55:06.178 --> 55:10.598
I was just wondering which law firm
I should hire this time.

55:10.599 --> 55:12.726
- Is that something to be proud of?
-  I mean,

55:13.393 --> 55:14.977
it's nothing to brag about, but--

55:14.978 --> 55:17.063
She won't be able to act for now.

55:17.064 --> 55:18.899
She knows pursuing you would implicate me,

55:19.399 --> 55:20.983
which would only escalate matters.

55:25.739 --> 55:29.201
But wouldn't you say
that was quite a display?

55:29.785 --> 55:30.993
What was?

55:30.994 --> 55:32.120
Everyone saw it.

55:32.788 --> 55:35.958
The Queen Mother talked about tarnishing
my reputation or whatever.

55:36.458 --> 55:38.209
And you taking my side.

55:40.963 --> 55:42.463
Wake up.

55:42.464 --> 55:44.299
Palace staff do not divulge
palace affairs.

55:47.427 --> 55:48.971
Do you really believe that?

55:50.639 --> 55:54.058
They say the mouth is
the gateway to disaster,

55:54.059 --> 55:56.853
and the tongue is
a blade that cuts the body.

55:57.354 --> 55:59.606
Do you know how many mouths were there?

56:02.442 --> 56:07.239
And you think not a single mouth there
has loose lips?

56:10.409 --> 56:14.496
They probably whipped up
an entire soap opera out of it by now.

56:17.499 --> 56:18.916
I can't believe it.

56:18.917 --> 56:20.836
And still in his ceremonial robe?

56:21.503 --> 56:22.795
I mean, it makes sense.

56:22.796 --> 56:24.839
I heard from an attendant
of the Queen Mother…

56:24.840 --> 56:26.757
I thought it was just a passing scandal,

56:26.758 --> 56:29.677
but as soon as she fainted,
he swept her up in his arms.

56:29.678 --> 56:30.970
It caused quite a stir.

56:30.971 --> 56:32.763
It must be true love!

56:32.764 --> 56:34.098
I know, right?

56:34.099 --> 56:35.433
Hmm.

56:35.434 --> 56:37.226
Plenty of people weren't there.

56:37.227 --> 56:39.270
That doesn't make someone a suspect.

56:39.271 --> 56:41.231
She must've been
so shocked that she fainted.

56:44.318 --> 56:46.736
Your Majesty, are you all right?

56:46.737 --> 56:49.238
Please stay there. I will clean this up.

56:49.239 --> 56:50.406
Court Lady Im.

56:50.407 --> 56:51.699
Is anyone out there?

56:51.700 --> 56:52.909
Court Lady Im!

56:57.039 --> 56:58.832
What are your thoughts?

56:59.625 --> 57:00.750
Pardon?

57:00.751 --> 57:02.002
About what, Your Majesty?

57:03.378 --> 57:05.546
The Grand Prince and that maiden.

57:05.547 --> 57:07.257
Did they seem

57:08.592 --> 57:10.093
genuine in your eyes as well?
:cue

57:20.187 --> 57:22.313
- You're not coming with me?
- I have to work.

57:22.314 --> 57:23.523
But it's the weekend.

57:24.066 --> 57:25.067
If I clock out,

57:26.193 --> 57:27.401
someone will kill me.

57:27.402 --> 57:28.737
Who?

57:30.614 --> 57:31.990
Him.

57:33.200 --> 57:35.327
Oh.

57:36.328 --> 57:38.080
Try not to stay up too late, though.

57:38.664 --> 57:39.830
I shall try.

57:39.831 --> 57:41.999
You can call me
if you have trouble sleeping.

57:42.000 --> 57:43.377
I shall.

57:54.721 --> 57:56.306
The more mouths, the better, right?

58:47.065 --> 58:48.149
Your Ladyship!

58:51.945 --> 58:53.612
Are you all right?

58:53.613 --> 58:55.782
What about His Royal Highness?
Is he all right?

58:57.075 --> 58:58.076
Well…

59:00.203 --> 59:02.246
Our dear Steward Kim played a huge role.

59:02.247 --> 59:04.623
I am quite a biker, you see.

59:04.624 --> 59:06.126
Thank you.

59:07.377 --> 59:08.502
Ha!

59:08.503 --> 59:09.670
Applause please.

59:12.424 --> 59:14.175
Well done!

59:14.176 --> 59:15.259
All right!

59:15.260 --> 59:16.303
I'm exhausted.

59:39.826 --> 59:41.036
Still alive?

59:41.661 --> 59:43.580
For now.

59:45.040 --> 59:47.541
I haven't been able to eat,
so I'm starving.

59:47.542 --> 59:50.085
Why not? Is the food not to your liking?

59:50.086 --> 59:51.630
No, I'm just trying to lose weight.

59:52.130 --> 59:53.339
Why?

59:53.340 --> 59:55.424
Looking gaunt will make me
seem more like a victim.

59:58.178 --> 01:00:00.263
You'll have the Royal Guard
starting tomorrow.

01:00:00.889 --> 01:00:01.890
Really?

01:00:02.390 --> 01:00:04.391
Is that allowed
when we're not married yet?

01:00:04.392 --> 01:00:05.684
It isn't.

01:00:05.685 --> 01:00:06.728
I see.

01:00:07.229 --> 01:00:09.856
"Another crazy stunt pulled
by the infatuated Grand Prince"?

01:00:10.690 --> 01:00:12.650
I guess you can put it like that.

01:00:17.113 --> 01:00:18.490
Should I pull one too?

01:01:34.149 --> 01:01:36.400
Never thought I'd be doing this.

01:01:50.957 --> 01:01:54.794
This is the least we can do
to make them think we're madly in love.

01:01:56.212 --> 01:01:57.255
Oh, right.

01:02:01.843 --> 01:02:02.844
Here.

01:02:04.137 --> 01:02:06.640
This is the tea I drink
when I have trouble sleeping.

01:02:07.265 --> 01:02:09.225
It's really expensive, so don't waste it.
:cue

01:02:10.936 --> 01:02:12.896
One more thing…

01:02:15.273 --> 01:02:18.360
This is the magnesium supplement
I take when I really can't asleep.

01:02:19.235 --> 01:02:22.864
The side effect is nightmares,
but it's better than not sleeping at all.

01:02:25.951 --> 01:02:27.827
- When did I ever ask--
- Stop that.

01:02:28.745 --> 01:02:31.164
You didn't see a doctor
after what happened, did you?

01:02:35.752 --> 01:02:38.713
Don't you think I'd be
quite the supportive wife?

01:02:40.298 --> 01:02:41.383
Hmm.

01:03:03.071 --> 01:03:04.155
What are you doing?

01:03:12.747 --> 01:03:13.748
Stay still.

01:03:53.163 --> 01:03:56.082
PERFECT CROWN

01:04:32.160 --> 01:04:34.036
Why would I blush

01:04:34.037 --> 01:04:36.955
and get all fluttery over a measly kiss?

01:04:36.956 --> 01:04:39.291
You should have maintained decorum.

01:04:39.292 --> 01:04:41.795
Then what? Should we make it
a shotgun wedding?

01:04:43.004 --> 01:04:45.882
Can I take you somewhere?
Let's speed things up a bit.

01:04:46.466 --> 01:04:49.094
The quicker we get married,
the quicker we get divorced.

01:04:50.053 --> 01:04:51.136
Smile!

01:04:51.137 --> 01:04:53.890
Do you have that much time
- to waste?
- I don't.

01:04:54.516 --> 01:04:57.392
That maiden
should move out of your private residence.

01:04:57.393 --> 01:05:00.230
Do you have a plan?

01:05:01.022 --> 01:05:02.397
Seong Huiju, what's wrong?

01:05:02.398 --> 01:05:05.275
Jeongwoo! The brakes aren't working!

01:05:11.032 --> 01:05:13.326
Why aren't you answering?

01:05:13.993 --> 01:05:16.370
Will you take their side and not mine

01:05:16.371 --> 01:05:18.413
because they're your family?

01:05:23.253 --> 01:05:24.420
I will take your side.

01:05:33.263 --> 01:05:34.347
I must appear

01:05:35.306 --> 01:05:36.850
insanely infatuated with you…

01:05:45.859 --> 01:05:47.235
…for people to believe

01:05:49.154 --> 01:05:50.738
this absurd marriage is genuine.

01:06:07.839 --> 01:06:09.841
- What's that?
- It's my hopae.

01:06:10.842 --> 01:06:11.843
What about it?

01:06:13.261 --> 01:06:15.387
Use it when you need a title behind you

01:06:15.388 --> 01:06:16.514
or when you are afraid.

01:06:18.850 --> 01:06:21.811
Does it summon a dragon
if I swing it around or something?

01:06:29.777 --> 01:06:30.778
It'll summon me.

01:06:42.040 --> 01:06:44.042
Translated by Justin S. Kim

01:06:55.345 --> 01:06:59.057
PERFECT CROWN
